 Objective: To delineate the epidemiological profile of HIV seropositive patients on antiretroviral therapy at the Clinical Hospital of the Federal University of Goias.

 Methods: The present study is documental and analitical descriptive and it was conducted at the Clinical Hospital of the Federal University of Goias, trough data collection of 222 records of individuals in drug therapy.

 Data were collected regarding the personal aspects, aspects related to the infection and information about the most used therapeutic.

